      "text": [
        "3701 - وَ - فِي خَبَرٍ آخَرَ : \"إِنِ اِسْتَحْلَفَهُ عَلَى مَا أَخَذَ مِنْهُ فَجَائِزٌ لَهُ أَنْ يَحْلِفَ إِذَا قَالَ هَذِهِ اَلْكَلِمَةَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3701 - And in another narration: \"If he makes him swear regarding what he took from him, then it is permissible for him to swear if he says this statement.\""
        ]
      }
    }
